race.description: Just Energy - All Your Solar Needs Mdn Plate
race.comment: ZOUDEADLY (9) is a three start maiden who has found the line nicely at the last two over sharper journeys. Looks suited out in ground now and could be tough to stop. DRUTHERS (14) was well fancied on debut and was beaten for speed, settling last but kept finding the line. Kept fresh and slightly longer journey suits. Will be winding up late. POL ROGEUR (7) settled off pace on debut and kept finding the line, finishing third. Can only be improved.  IT'S GNARLY (15) was in the market on debut and pushed forward from a wide draw, leading into the lane before fading late over 1200m at Sale on February 1. Promising type who is sure to measure up with the blinkers added.
